title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Ed Sheeran Gave Bad Real Estate Advice
description: One Oscar winner says you should always go up to a celebrity and talk to them… she learned that lesson after missing her own opportunity. And we’ve got another person looking to get money from Ed Sheeran off a bad real estate deal. At least this time it’s not a legal matter and Ed can laugh about it.
